ing: 1/2 bunch kale - stems removed and discarded, leaves torn into bite-size pieces
4 cubes ice, or more if desired
n: Kale, Banana, and Peanut Butter Smoothie
des: "My own little concoction for a quick and healthy snack on the go."
ins: Blend bananas, almond milk, kale, ice, and peanut butter in a blender until smooth.
